{[#]} {[%tqu "En","Black to move.","","","c6f3","This is the right moment to capture on f3. Yes, it's a small concession, but White had to spend a tempo (Qe2) to provoke it.",10]} 9... Bxf3 $1 {This is the right moment to capture on f3. Yes, it's a small concession, but White had to spend a tempo (Qe2) to provoke it.} (9... O-O $6 {after 9.Re1, castle works very well, but here the situation is different for concrete reasons:} 10. Ne5 $1 Nxe5 11. dxe5 Qd5 12. f4 $1 $16 {[%csl Ge2,Yg2][%cal Ye2g2] The queen defends g2, big difference.}) 10. Qxf3 c6 $132 {It is too early for ...c5, but White wasted a tempo with the queen and also the knight on g3 is not fantastic.} *

